Women’s pole vault world U20 champion 🥳

Congratulations to @mire_reinstorf who broke her PB to secure the gold medal for South Africa 🇿🇦 

#Athletics #TrackAndField #PoleVault #SouthAfrica

node.text:
Will @letsile_tebogo become the fastest teenager in the world? 

The Botswanan blazed to a 10.11 clocking in the @wau20nairobi21 100m semis.  Can he beat @adamgemili’s championship record of 10.05 in the final?👀

#WorldAthleticsU20 #Athletics #TrackAndField #Track #Botswana
